A Hadoop job to do letter frequency analysis ( http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Letter_frequency).

The Hadoop job is run using Spring-Hadoop http://www.springsource.org/spring-data/hadoop.

RunLetterFreqStandalone.java runs the Hadoop job in standalone mode.

RunLetterFreqScript.java runs the Hadoop job in Pseudo distributed or distributed mode.

Below is sample output :


